{"tid":663411,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"港女為咗食洋腸可以無晒要求👀","createTime":"2018-05-13T09:31:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T10:59:26.000Z","uid":5190,"like":54,"dislike":118,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"a8bd7af3fb3cff35479dfa21cab4a7dfaa06ab39","tid":663411,"uid":5190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T09:31:34.000Z","msg":"食洋腸 一係為咗條撚長啲 一係想要得大隻鬼佬 又要靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家啲港女為咗食洋腸 已經無晒理智 只要你係鬼仔就要得落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啱先見到有條港女 染晒金毛 著啲仆街平時係屋企著嘅背心熱褲 拖住個鬼仔 咁你要做abc我阻止唔到你 你老味 條鬼仔瘦到成條柴咁 港男稍微有打過波都大隻過佢個種 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔係特別高 俾盡180<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行起上嚟完全無鬼佬feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  真係貪佢碌鳩長咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再望一望佢個樣 都係普通鬼仔樣 係就係血統優良 樣都靚過亞腸 但港男十個都有一個叫好樣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n為咗要血統 無晒要求 睇下你班港女幾低賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463df6947c0ea0820ad6b74ecbf292d00a01f7c9","tid":663411,"uid":58254,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T09:32:31.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bea5209a4e75f4ad618a143975a884d0beeddf8","tid":663411,"uid":5190,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"463df6947c0ea0820ad6b74ecbf292d00a01f7c9","tid":663411,"uid":58254,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T09:32:31.000Z","msg":"係咁架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T09:33:04.000Z","msg":"所以你話港女幾cheap<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"